flowRoot.flowPara: The French interpretation "Ciel Volé" on the other hand, is a parable explaining, that the upper ranks in the mainframe are trying to make the lower ranks having no sight in the mainframe.

In the so-called "Chemtrail" conspiracy, is "offered" by Google, as soon as one falls out of the standard consumer behavior. In fact it's only a technical test of a boing plane. In order to be able to shift the weight of the aeroplain, it has pumps and water tanks. "Switching on the toxic sprays" is simply the transition into an air layer (at Mach 1) with more humidity.
As an ally but unfortunately also by some to mistreat
(Anononymous ⇨ Case Dusty; where I would expected, that Kenny "learned" violence eg from his father?)
Like a plush: to hug, pet and care for

Clinical use: as a coping strategy, e.g. you can buy a shy cat for a scared child, which then helps the child to analyze his fears without focussing directly on his own fears, that then might would lead to a thought blockade & avoidance behavior instead of the things that caused the fear and to analyze them objectively
